{{vgname|孤独的托马斯|en=Thomas Was Alone}}是由迈克·比瑟尔创作的[[平台游戏|益智平台游戏]]，最早于2010年10月作为[[Flash游戏|Flash游戏]]发布<ref name="blitz">{{cite web | url = http://www.blitz1up.com/articles/full_article/137 | title = Thomas was alone. An indie game created in 24 hours | publisher = [[Blitz_Games|Blitz Games]] | date = 18 October 2010 | access-date = 14 November 2012 | url-status = yes | archive-url = https://archive.is/20110721025733/http://www.blitz1up.com/articles/full_article/137 | archive-date = 2011-07-21 }}</ref>。游戏后经完善，2012年7月于[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[OS_X|OS X]]平台发行。此后游戏又于[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Wii_U|Wii U]]、[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]等平台发行。[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]版预定于2021年2月发行。

